  - Using API
  - Text to sequence
  - Tokenizer
  - Padding
  - Exercise: Explore the BBC news archive

Module 2: Word Embeddings
  - TensorFlow datasets
  - Exercise: BBC news archive

Module 3: Sequence Models
  - Implementing LSTM
  - Accuracy and loss
  - Using a convolutional network
  - Exercise: Exploring overfitting in NLP

Module 4: Sequence models and literature
  - Sequence models and literature
  - Generate poetry
  - Exercise: Using LSTMS to write Shakespeares
